      <tr><td>Non-oil GDP growth</td><td>7.6%</td><td>Bank of Ghana March 2026</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Inflation (February 2026)</td><td>3.3% (lowest since August 1999)</td><td>GSS</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Policy rate</td><td>14.0% (cut 150 bps, March 18)</td><td>Bank of Ghana</td></tr>
